===Noun===
[[Image:Grass-JW.jpg|thumb|right|Grass.]]
{{en-noun|es|-}}

# {{context|countable|uncountable}} Any [[plant]] of the [[family]] [[Poaceae]], characterized by [[leaves]] that arise from [[node]]s in the [[stem]], wrap around it for a distance, and leave, especially those grown as [[ground cover]] rather than for [[grain]].
# A [[lawn]].
# {{context|slang|uncountable}} [[marijuana|Marijuana]].
# {{slang}} An [[informer]], police informer; one who betrays a group (of criminals, etc) to the authorities.

